The data I looked at this week is all the Love Island USA couples

library(tidyverse)
library(rvest)
library(jsonlite)


url8 &lt;- "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Love_Island_USA_season_8"
url7 &lt;- "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Love_Island_USA_season_7"
